long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Clone Robot is a fun arcade game where we try to progress and get points by overcoming obstacles with clone robots.
There are clone robots in the game. With these robots, we move forward by overcoming the obstacles we encounter. We get points by carefully advancing the challenges and continuing the competition by maintaining our high score goal. Clone Robot has emerged as a skill game designed with us. In mind for those who love robot games and challenge us.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Clone Robot  Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
